ding-snug tracking-tighter text-primary max-lg:text-xl">Remote configuration</h3><p class="text-base leading-normal font-light text-gray-800 max-xl:leading-snug">Remotely manage your pricing and products without shipping an app update.</p></div></div></div></li><li class="relative overflow-hidden border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-5 px-6 pb-6 max-xl:rounded-xl max-xl:p-4 max-xl:px-5 max-xl:pb-5 max-sm:p-4" style="background:linear-gradient(#f9f9fb, #f9f9fb) padding-box, linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(184, 224, 207, 1) 0%, rgba(234, 237, 246, 0) 100%) border-box, linear-gradient(#eaedf6, #eaedf6) border-box"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute top-0 -left-7.5 rounded-full opacity-[0.5] blur-[120px] size-50 max-xl:-left-20 max-xl:size-42.5 max-lg:-left-15 max-lg:size-35 bg-[#C1F6E0]" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col gap-10 max-xl:gap-8 max-lg:gap-4"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6.5 max-xl:gap-5 max-lg:gap-4.5 max-sm:gap-3.5"><div class="flex size-15 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/80 max-xl:size-14 max-lg:size-12 max-sm:size-11 shadow-feature-green text-secondary-green" aria-hidden="true"><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center [&amp;_svg]:size-full size-7 max-xl:size-6.5 max-lg:size-6 max-sm:size-5" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 28 28"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21.906 12.719 26.5 8.125l-4.594-1.531L20.375 2l-4.594 4.594.919 2.91-1.531 1.53c-1.378-.918-3.063-1.53-4.747-1.53C5.828 9.655 2 13.483 2 18.077S5.828 26.5 10.422 26.5s8.422-3.828 8.422-8.422c0-1.837-.613-3.369-1.532-4.747l1.532-1.531zm-6.125 5.36c0 2.909-2.45 5.358-5.36 5.358-2.908 0-5.358-2.45-5.358-5.359 0-2.91 2.45-5.36 5.359-5.36.919 0 1.837.307 2.603.613L9.35 17.006c-.612.613-.612 1.532 0 2.144.306.306.766.46 1.072.46s.765-.154 1.072-.46l3.675-3.675c.306.766.612 1.684.612 2.603"></path></svg></span></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 max-xl:gap-2.5 max-lg:gap-2"><h3 class="font-object text-2xl leading-snug tracking-tighter text-primary max-lg:text-xl">Ship what matters</h3><p class="text-base leading-normal font-light text-gray-800 max-xl:leading-snug">No more post-WWDC-scramble: we handle changes to Apple and Google’s APIs so you don’t have to.</p></div></div></div></li><li class="relative overflow-hidden border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-5 px-6 pb-6 max-xl:rounded-xl max-xl:p-4 max-xl:px-5 max-xl:pb-5 max-sm:p-4" style="background:linear-gradient(#f9f9fb, #f9f9fb) padding-box, linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(184, 194, 224, 1) 0%, rgba(234, 237, 246, 0) 100%) border-box, linear-gradient(#eaedf6, #eaedf6) border-box"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute top-0 -left-7.5 rounded-full opacity-[0.5] blur-[120px] size-50 max-xl:-left-20 max-xl:size-42.5 max-lg:-left-15 max-lg:size-35 bg-[#C1C9F6]" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex h-full flex-col gap-10 max-xl:gap-8 max-lg:gap-4"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6.5 max-xl:gap-5 max-lg:gap-4.5 max-sm:gap-3.5"><div class="flex size-15 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/80 max-xl:size-14 max-lg:size-12 max-sm:size-11 shadow-feature-blue text-secondary-blue-1" aria-hidden="true"><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center [&amp;_svg]:size-full size-7 max-xl:size-6.5 max-lg:size-6 max-sm:size-5" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 28 28"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.86" d="M24.126 3H4.014A2.014 2.014 0 0 0 2 5.014v11.493c0 1.112.902 2.014 2.014 2.014h20.112a2.014 2.014 0 0 0 2.014-2.014V5.014A2.014 2.014 0 0 0 24.126 3Z"></path><path fill="currentColor" d="M7.246 13.275a2.514 2.514 0 1 0 0-5.028 2.514 2.514 0 0 0 0 5.028M22.689 8.247h-3.592a.72.72 0 0 0-.718.718v3.591c0 .397.322.719.718.719h3.592a.72.72 0 0 0 .718-.719V8.965a.72.72 0 0 0-.718-.718M12.274 11.837a1.077 1.077 0 1 0 0-2.155 1.077 1.077 0 0 0 0 2.155M15.865 11.839a1.077 1.077 0 1 0 0-2.155 1.077 1.