4 0v1.227c-5.289.546-9.504 4.762-10.05 10.05H1.553a1.167 1.167 0 0 0 0 2.334h1.228c.546 5.29 4.761 9.505 10.05 10.05v1.228a1.167 1.167 0 0 0 2.334 0v-1.227c5.288-.546 9.504-4.762 10.05-10.05h1.227a1.167 1.167 0 0 0 0-2.334M13.998 22.954c-4.931 0-8.945-4.013-8.945-8.945 0-4.93 4.014-8.944 8.945-8.944 4.93 0 8.944 4.013 8.944 8.944s-4.013 8.945-8.944 8.945"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="crosshairs_inline_svg__a"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 0h28v28H0z"></path></clipPath></defs></svg></span></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 max-xl:gap-2.5 max-lg:gap-2"><h3 class="font-object text-2xl leading-snug tracking-tighter text-primary max-lg:text-xl">A/B paywall testing</h3><p class="text-base leading-normal font-light text-gray-800 max-xl:leading-snug">RevenueCat Experiments offers easy-to-deploy A/B testing and also displays and measures how your experiments impact your full subscription funnel.</p></div></div></div></li></ul></div></section><section class="section-spacing h-40 max-xl:h-30 max-lg:h-28 max-md:h-20 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-social-proof bg-white"><article class="mx-auto flex max-w-210 gap-10 max-xl:max-w-180 max-xl:gap-8 max-lg:items-center max-lg:gap-6 max-md:max-w-none max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-7 max-md:px-4"><h2 class="sr-only">Mojo<!-- -->&#x27;s case study</h2><div class="flex size-52.5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-4xl border border-transparent p-6 shadow-case-gradient-logo backdrop-blur-md max-xl:size-42.5 max-lg:size-34.5 max-md:w-full gradient-social-proof-logo-white"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="size-26 object-contain max-xl:size-22 max-lg:size-18 max-md:size-20" style="color:transparent" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/cfefe435412dff8b62891cab0c648ca68d9acea8-80x80.svg?w=96&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 1x, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/cfefe435412dff8b62891cab0c648ca68d9acea8-80x80.svg?w=256&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 2x" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/cfefe435412dff8b62891cab0c648ca68d9acea8-80x80.svg?w=256&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format"/></div><blockquote class="flex flex-col justify-center"><div class="font-object -tracking-wider text-balance text-primary text-[30px] max-xl:text-[26px] max-lg:text-[22px] max-md:text-lg"><p>“We have gotten back so much time to focus on important features thanks to RevenueCat!”</p></div><cite class="mt-6 text-lg leading-tight not-italic max-xl:mt-5 max-lg:mt-4 max-md:mt-3 max-md:text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-primary">Francescu Santoni<!-- -->, </span><span class="text-gray-750">CTO at mojo.video</span></cite><a class="font-object inline-flex items-center gap-x-1 rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:transition-transform [&amp;_svg]:duration-300 hover:[&amp;_svg]:translate-x-0.5 mt-6 font-medium max-xl:mt-5 max-lg:mt-4 max-md:mt-3 max-md:text-sm" href="/customers/mojo-case">Read case study<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 7 9" class="w-2!"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="m0 9.002 6.998-3.844V3.844L0 0v1.711l5.08 2.79L0 7.291z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></blockquote></article></section><section class="section-spacing h-40 max-xl:h-30 max-lg:h-28 max-md:h-20 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-spacing h-40 max-xl:h-30 max-lg:h-28 max-md:h-20 bg-gray-50" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-split bg-gray-50"><div class="container"><div class="flex max-lg:items-center max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-8 flex-row"><div class="mx-auto flex w-full shrink flex-col justify-center max-md:items-center max-md:px-0 max-md:text-center pr-24 max-xl:pr-13"><h2 class="font-object leading-dense font-medium tracking-tighter text-balance text-primary max-w-4xl max-lg:max-w-2xl max-md:max-w-xl text-[3rem] max-lg:text-[2rem] max-sm:text-[1.625rem] text-left max-md:text-center">Explore the Dashboard</h2><div class="mt-4 max-w-2xl space-y-3 pr-4 text-xl leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-pretty text-gray-800 max-xl:mt-3 max-xl:text-lg max-md:max-w-md max-md:px-0 max-md:text-base md:max-w-lg [&amp;_strong]:font-normal [&amp;&gt;:is(ul,ol):first-child]:mt-0"><ul class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-4 max-xl:mt-5 max-lg:mt-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">RevenueCat’s dashboard is your command center for all things in-app purchases.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">Get an overview of KPIs or dig deeper with configurable data visualizations in <a class="font-object inline-flex items-center gap-x-1 rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 max-md:text-sm font-medium max-xl:mt-4 max-md:mt-3" href="/feature/charts">Charts</a>.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">With <a class="font-object inline-flex items-center gap-x-1 rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 max-md:text-sm font-medium max-xl:mt-4 max-md:mt-3" href="/feature/customer-management">Customers</a>, gain a deeper understanding of customer behavior and enable better support with centralized access to cross-platform customer data.</span></li></ul></div><a class="font-object inline-flex items-center rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 max-md:text-sm [&amp;_svg]:transition-transform [&amp;_svg]:duration-300 hover:[&amp;_svg]:translate-x-0.5 mt-6 w-max gap-2 font-medium max-md:mx-auto max-md:mt-5" href="https://demo.revenuecat.com/overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Try the demo<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 7 9" class="w-2!"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="m0 9.002 6.998-3.844V3.844L0 0v1.711l5.08 2.79L0 7.291z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></div><div class="relative w-full max-lg:w-full pointer-events-none max-sm:w-screen"><div class="flex aspect-auto items-center justify-center"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="1171" height="790" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="drop-shadow-illustration" style="color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=640&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 640w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=750&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 750w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=828&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 828w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 1080w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 1200w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 1920w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 2048w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format 3840w" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c3qnx9b0/production/325a275ef084065470f10a3edf097d9ed84fca8b-1171x790.png?w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;auto=format"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-spacing h-16 max-md:h-8 bg-gray-50" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-spacing h-16 max-md:h-8 bg-gray-50" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-split bg-gray-50"><div class="container"><div class="flex max-lg:items-center max-md:flex-col max-md:gap-8 flex-row-reverse"><div class="mx-auto flex w-full shrink flex-col justify-center max-md:items-center max-md:px-0 max-md:text-center pl-24 max-xl:pl-13"><h2 class="font-object leading-dense font-medium tracking-tighter text-balance text-primary max-w-4xl max-lg:max-w-2xl max-md:max-w-xl text-[2.5rem] max-lg:text-[1.75rem] max-sm:text-[1.5rem] text-left max-md:text-center">Proactively improve your product</h2><div class="mt-4 max-w-2xl space-y-3 pr-4 text-xl leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-pretty text-gray-800 max-xl:mt-3 max-xl:text-lg max-md:max-w-md max-md:px-0 max-md:text-base md:max-w-lg [&amp;_strong]:font-normal [&amp;&gt;:is(ul,ol):first-child]:mt-0"><ul class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-4 max-xl:mt-5 max-lg:mt-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">Reduce the engineering and support workload with the <a class="font-object inline-flex items-center gap-x-1 rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 max-md:text-sm font-medium max-xl:mt-4 max-md:mt-3" href="/feature/customer-center">Customer Center</a>, a self-serve subscription hub for your customers</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">Understand why customers churn with cancellation surveys to inform product decisions</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="flex h-6 shrink-0 items-center" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-4 text-secondary-blue-1"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.33" d="m13.333 4-7.334 7.333L2.666 8"></path></svg></span><span class="text-left text-lg leading-snug font-light tracking-dense text-gray-800 max-lg:text-base [&amp;_a]:!mt-0">Prevent churn by showing an attractive offer right before customers cancel their plans</span></li></ul></div><a class="font-object inline-flex items-center rounded transition-colors duration-300 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 text-secondary-blue-1 hover:text-secondary-blue-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-4 max-md:text-sm [&amp;_svg]:transition-transform [&amp;_svg]:duration-300 hover:[&amp;_svg]:translate-x-0.5 mt-6 w-max gap-2 font-medium max-md:mx-auto max-md:mt-5" href="https://app.revenuecat.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get started<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 7 9" class="w-2!"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="m0 9.002 6.998-3.844V3.844L0 0v1.711l5.08 2.79L0 7.291z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></div><div class="relative w-full max-lg:w-full pointer-events-none max-sm:w-screen"><div class="relative size-full aspect-[498/478] mx-auto max-w-[498px]"><div class="aspect-[498/478] w-full absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-1/2"><div class="" style="width:100%;height:100%"><canvas style="vertical-align:top;width:0;height:0"></canvas></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-spacing h-40 max-xl:h-30 max-lg:h-28 max-md:h-20 bg-gray-50" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-spacing h-40 max-xl:h-30 max-lg:h-28 max-md:h-20 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"></section><section class="section-feature-list bg-white"><div class="container"><header class="mb-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center max-md:mb-10 max-md:gap-3.5 max-sm:mb-9 max-sm:items-start"><h2 class="font-object leading-dense font-medium tracking-tighter text-balance text-primary max-w-4xl max-lg:max-w-2xl max-md:max-w-xl text-[3.5rem] max-xl:text-[2.75rem] max-lg:text-[2.25rem] max-sm:text-[1.875rem] text-center mx-auto">How it works</h2></header><ul class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-30 max-xl:gap-9 max-md:mx-auto max-md:max-w-md max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-11"><li class="flex flex-col gap-4"><div class="flex flex-col gap-6.5 max-xl:gap-5 max-lg:gap-4.5 max-sm:gap-3.5"><di